<sect2 status="final" id="infoline">

  <title>Image infos line</title>

  <indexterm>
    <primary>darkroom panels</primary>
    <secondary>image infos</secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <indexterm>
    <primary>image infos</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <informaltable frame="none">
    <tgroup cols="2" colsep="0" rowsep="0">
      <colspec colwidth="6*"/>
      <colspec colwidth="4*"/>
      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>
            You can display a line with very important image infos.
          </entry>
          <entry>
            <graphic fileref="darkroom/images/infoline.png" scalefit="1" width="80%" align="center" />
          </entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>
    The content of this line can be set in preferences (see <xref linkend="darkroom_options"/>).
    Available variables are the same as for the export module (see <xref linkend="export_selected_usage_filename"/>).
    You can also add new lines by using <code>$(NL)</code> variable.
  </para>

  <para>
    Position of the infos line can also be set in preferences (see <xref linkend="darkroom_options"/>).
  </para>
</sect2>
